Dialogs.Dialog: Manaka
Hey, can I ask you a question？
What？
Am I... good enough？
Eh！？
Sometimes I feel uneasy. I wonder why you chose me. I wonder what part of me you like, and stuff.
...Perhaps there might be a girl that suits you much better...
Stop！
Stop imagining things without considering my feelings！
Ah... That's right... I'm sorry.
(Hmm... How can I make you understand this ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
About what we talked about earlier, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Manaka
...Yeah.
Why do you love me？ There might be a guy that suits you better than me, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
T-There is no one who can take your place...！
I see. Then you can rest assured, because I feel the same way too.
It's not just some parts of you that I like. If I had to say, it would be everything about you.
And you feel the same way, right？
...Not at all. It's not the same...
I definitely love you more... I'm not losing to you.
All right. From now on, we'll see who wins, okay？
Manaka
Have you ever thought about the mechanisms of falling in love？
Hmm, before I realized it, I already loved you. That's why I said yes when you confessed to me, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
I'm so happy. Anyway, even though you said so, there are things that I'm quite concerned about.
Ah, no. I didn't mean that I feel unsatisfied or uneasy...
I'm just wondering where these feelings of love come from...
For me, I've never really hated anyone in my life. But I've never loved anyone this much either.
That's why I think that love is amazing, and I wonder what are behind these feelings of love.
(It really is amazing...)
Manaka
We've talked about the mechanisms of falling in love earlier, right？
Yeah. Did you find the answer？
Hmm... No matter how hard I think about it, I can never understand it.
But, I recalled some people saying that love doesn't need reason.
When I think about it, it's really true. So, it's probably better that I just stop thinking about this.
Is that so？
Yeah, I know there are many theories about love, but I don't care anymore.
Just being able to see you is the only answer I need.
...Yeah.
Hehe. Thanks for listening to me. Ah, I spent too much time thinking about this that I've slacked off on studying lately！
Manaka
It's almost your birthday, huh？
Ah, it's coming up soon.
Yes, it is. Geez... Are guys always like this？
What do you mean？
Do guys usually not pay attention to their own birthday？
I don't know. What about you ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yeah. I always get excited about my birthday.
It's another year for me to grow older and experience new things.
I can't help but think about what will be coming next and whether I'll meet new people.
I see. You really think a lot about your birthday...
Hey, how come the topic was changed to my birthday？ We were talking about your birthday to begin with！
Manaka
Hey, about your birthday...
...Geez. You forgot about it.
Hahaha. I'm more concerned about your birthday ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Really？
Of course. I've been thinking about it a lot. Even now.
...Hmm.
That's your response？ Just that？
What do you mean by "just that"？
Ah, you're getting embarrassed.
...I am not. It's not about my birthday. I was talking about yours. Geez！
(I wonder what she's planning for my birthday.)
Manaka
Huh...
What？ Is it about my birthday？
Hmm？ You remember it？
Y-Yeah, I remember.
...Hehe, geez. I wish you just forgot about it.
Shall I？
You just try to play along, huh？ Geez, someone like you... Hehehe！
By the way, you seem to think about it a lot. Did you get anything for me yet？
I wish I did.
You didn't！？
Huh？ I thought you didn't care about it. Hehehe.
(Urgh, why is she the one teasing me now？)
Hey, for my birthday...
Manaka
Hmm？ Now, you've started to care about it, huh？
I've never said that I didn't care about it.
Okay, okay. Hmm, I can tell you that I already got something for you. Just don't expect too much.
No, I'm really expecting something nice.
Hehe, why？
Because you've been thinking about it for a long time. Even longer than I have.
....Because it's the day you were born. Isn't it something I should feel thankful for？
Oh well. I'll have to wait until your birthday to wish you a happy birthday, right！？
It's almost your birthday, huh, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
Ah, you remembered.
Yeah. Does your family have any plans for your birthday, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yeah. We always celebrate a family member's birthday together.
Like, do you bake a cake together？
Right. It's a Takane tradition to bake a cake for a family member whose birthday is coming up.
...You mean your dad also bakes a cake？
Of course. He's always in high spirits, and he takes a day off from work every year for the occasion.
He does！？
Hehe, Papa is very obsessed with stuff like this.
I wonder what kind of cake he'll make this year... I can't wait▼
(If I don't try my best, maybe she won't appreciate it when we celebrate her birthday together！)
Manaka
By the way, Papa told me that the cake he planned to bake for me this year would be something I've never tasted before.
E-Eh？ ...What kind of cake is that？
He wouldn't tell me.
I only know that he asked his friend in France to send him a secret recipe.
France！？
Yeah. I'm very happy but I think he overdid it. Anyway, he told me that he didn't want to lose.
...Lose to who？
For that, he didn't tell me and Mama only smiled as if it were something that couldn't be helped.
But I'm so curious what kind of cake it'll be... I really can't wait▼
(The one her dad doesn't want to lose to... Could it be...)
How was your dad after that？
Manaka
Seems like he practiced baking it once, but it didn't come out well. Mama said that he was quite disappointed.
I see...
And then he asked about you.
Eh...？ About me？
Yeah, like whether you knew my birthday, and whether you had said something about it...
When I asked him why he was concerned about that, he said he was just collecting information.
...What！！
I don't understand... Do you know why he said that？
(As I thought, his rival is me！)
Your birthday is coming up.
Manaka
Yeah, I hope it'll be a special one this year.
A special one？
Yeah, we've been talking about my birthday all this time until now, right？
And you've been very concerned about it for so long. Actually, that's already more than enough for me.
Now I'm in trouble.
Eh？
At least, I want you to anticipate something from me. That way I can keep trying my best for you.
Hmm？ So I can anticipate something nice？
Y-Yeah.
Hehe！ Okay, I'll do as you wish. You have to try very hard, all right？
(I won't lose to your dad！)
Manaka
It's been almost a year, huh？
Really？ It's been a year already？
...Hmm？ You realized it at once, huh？
Well, I should, right？
Hehe, sorry. I didn't mean to tease you.
It feels like just a blink of an eye, right？ Since the time we started dating...
When I recall the moment I confessed to you, I still feel so embarrassed.
I was really happy when you confessed to me, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Hey, don't say it... Please, I beg you. Don't look at me now.
(You've never changed, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Manaka
Hey, usually, what do people do when it's time for an important occasion？
Ah, you mean for our anniversary？
Yeah, this is my first time to be in a relationship, so I don't really know...
Hmm... What shall we do？
When you speak that way, I kind of wonder if you've already had plans in your mind.
Hahaha. Exactly.
Well, we don't really have to think about it too seriously, right？ Let's not pressure ourselves.
Hehe, we can treat everyday like our anniversary, huh？
Right. But the first anniversary should be special.
Yeah, I hope it would be something that we still think about no matter how many years have passed...
Manaka
Hey, how about we use this chance to tell each other if there's anything we want each other to improve？
To improve...？
...Nothing？
Hmm... How about you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Hmm, I don't have anything in particular, I think.
I don't have any either.
...Hehe. So, it seems our conversation ends here.
Haha, we'll just keep being nice to each other, okay？
Okay▼
Manaka
Hehe, our anniversary is coming up.
Yeah. Thanks for being nice to me this whole year.
Don't mention it. I have to thank you, too.
...Hehe.
Hahaha...
...I wish we could continue having a conversation like this forever.
Our next milestone is the next 3 years, okay？
No, 5 years！
Nah, 10 years！
Hehe, I want more！
Haha, right！ Let's try our best.
Okay▼
Manaka
...Can I ask you a question？
Yes, what？
Well... Is it really okay for you to have me by your side？
Eh！？
I'm sorry！
I think we're happy like this, but...
I don't if I'm the only one feeling happy. I'm so worried...
This is my first time to be in a relationship, so I don't really know anything.
...Sorry. I shouldn't say something like this anymore.
(How can I let you know how I feel...？)
About the question you asked me earlier, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Manaka
Is it really okay for you to have me by your side ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
How can it not be okay！？
I'm okay to have you by my side... No, I mean if it's not you, I can't...
I see. We both can rest assured then！
I see. We both can rest assured then！
Am I really good for you？
It has to be you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hey, come here.
...Okay！
Manaka
How can people love someone so much？
Huh？
I've been thinking about this lately. There's probably something special.
In the past, I didn't have any particular feelings for anyone. I just loved everyone and cared about everyone...
I used to be like that, but now...
I really don't know. Something must have changed inside me.
I wonder why I have this kind of feeling... This is mysterious.
(Um, I also wonder why...)
Manaka
Earlier, we talked about how people can love someone so much, right？
Yeah, did you find out the reason？
Yeah. For me, the answer is... because it's you.
Me？
...Right. If it wasn't you... I wouldn't have been able to love someone this much, for sure.
You are my first love, and the first person who made me feel this way...
I'm so glad that my first love is you. Thank you for always being by my side.
...No. This is like I'm confessing my love to you all over again.
But, this is really how I feel. Please let me love you like this forever, okay？
Manaka
Hey, it's almost your birthday, right？
Ah, now that you mentioned it...
Is there anything you want？
What I want？ Hmm...
I'll ask you again later, so think about it, okay？ ...Ah.
Huh？
For something like this, is it better that I keep it a secret？ You might want a surprise.
Hmm, a surprise is nice, too.
Really？ But I want you to be happy to get what you want...
Hmm, what should I do？ Hmm... Hmm...
(...She's just so cute like this. I'll keep watching her for a while.)
Have you decided whether you want to hear my request or not？
Manaka
Not yet... Can you give me some more time to think？
That's fine. For the meantime, I'll think about it more seriously too.
Hey, is it okay that you just give me some hints？
Hmm... But if I know beforehand what kind of thing I'll get, it won't be a surprise when I see it.
...Hmm, that's true.
But just some vague hints would be okay, right？
How about a chopstick rest？ Will you like it？ Or a doll？ That's not good, right？ Hey, which one do you like？
(I wouldn't call them vague hints...)
Well, my birthday's getting very close, huh...？
Manaka
Hmm...
Hahaha, it's okay. There's no need to rush.
I don't think you have to pay attention to it this much.
No, I have to.
It represents the day you were born into this world. It's a very important day.
Is it troublesome for you that I'm getting this happy about it？
No, not at all. I'm very thankful.
Okay. I was quite worried that I might cause you trouble. Now I'm a bit relieved.
I'll think about it carefully, so please just wait, okay？
Okay, roger that！
Manaka
I've decided.
Oh, so this is an official announcement, huh？
Hehe, I've decided to keep it a secret.
I see. Okay, I'll be looking forward to it then.
But, please don't expect too much, okay？
Eh？
Um... Um... I've really tried my best, but...
Hahaha, I was just kidding. When I have you with me, I don't need anything else, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
is this right？ ...T-Thank you...
Ah, I shouldn't be easily overjoyed like this, right？ Is it okay that I'm happy about it？
(For me, something like this is more than enough！)
It's almost your birthday, right, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
Yeah. Thank you for remembering it.
Has your family started talking about this？
Not yet. Hehe, you're pretty fast.
Hahaha, I see.
We bake some cake at home every year, but we don't really talk about it like this.
Don't tell me you bake your own birthday cakes, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
No, Papa is always the one baking it for me.
Huh？ So it's like that in your family, huh？
Yeah, it's quite thrilling every year. Hehe.
(Huh？ That means he's not very good at it, eh？)
Do you have a big birthday party at home ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
Not a big one, but there's always a party.
We eat cake, sing "Happy Birthday," and then I open the presents, something like that.
Our dinner will be a little bit more special. We reminisce about the old days while we're eating.
Reminisce about the old days？
Yeah, something about when I was in grade school or when Papa and Mama were young.
Hmm... That sounds fun.
Hehe, I usually stay up late on my birthday.
I'm hoping I can stay up even later this year.
Like, until 9:30 PM？
...I can stay longer than that... I think.
(But that's about your limit, isn't it...？)
Hey, do you have anything you want to ask from me ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
Hmm？ What do you mean？
Do you have any requests？ Like something you want or somewhere you want to visit？
Hmm... I don't have any.
Huh？ None at all？
Yes, just hearing you say "Happy Birthday" to me is enough.
Of course, I'll be saying that.
Hehe. Just that is more than enough. You don't have to concern yourself about it too much. Thank you.
(Hmm... What should I get for her then...？)
Manaka
About what you asked me earlier, whether I had a request for my birthday present or not...
Oh！ You've got something you want？
Yes... I want you.
Okay, that's good... What！？
One year from now, I want you to always be with me. And on my next birthday, I'll request the same thing. Is this not okay？
...I was just surprised. Of course, it's okay... But you want just this？
What do you mean by "just" this？
Because I'll always be with you no matter what, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
That's all I want to hear. Thank you. You've made me feel very happy even before my birthday has arrived.
You can look forward to my request every year, okay？
It's been a year, huh...？
Manaka
Hmm？ What？
Come on, it's almost a year since we started dating.
...Yeah. It went by very fast.
In the beginning, I kept thinking what it would feel like after a year has passed...
Nothing has changed, right？
Hmm？
No... To have you by my side, and to talk about this with you...
A lot of wonderful things have happened. Yeah.
(What was with that quiet moment？ I'm a bit concerned...)
Hey, earlier, we talked about what would happen after we've been together for a year, right？
Manaka
...Yeah.
At that time, was there something in your mind？
...Hehehe. I really can't hide anything from you...
To tell you the truth... I was about to tell you that I couldn't believe that you would still be with me after a year.
Eh！？
I don't have the confidence... I don't know if it's okay to be happy about what we are now...
...That was what I thought about back then...
Ah, but I'm okay now. After you said so many things to me, I've gained a little more confidence.
So, don't worry... Sorry for saying something weird.
(Just "a little" more confidence...？)
Is there anything about me you want me to improve, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
Hehe, why ask this all of a sudden？
Come on. We've been together for so long. Just tell me the truth.
Hmm... Maybe nothing？
Really？
...Yup.
No, there's something！
Eh？ Hey, this has happened before... How did you know what I was thinking？
That's because I'm your boyfriend.
...Hmm, is that so？
Now I have a lot more confidence...
(Yeah, this is going great！)
A year's passed, hasn't it？
Manaka
Yeah. Thank you for the past year. Um, I...
Huh？
Is it OK if I stay by your side like this for the next year, too？
Well, I want to continue being with you like this. So... please treat me kindly, okay？
Oh, same here. Please treat me well.
Okay▼
Manaka
Hey, I have a question.
Hmm？？ What is it？
...Do you regret that I became your girlfriend？
Why are you saying this all of a sudden...？ Did I do something bad？
No, it's not like that. It's just...
It's just, I don't think I have confidence in myself...
It's like I want to compensate for my own worthlessness. I feel like I still don't put enough effort.
I'm sorry. Just now, can you pretend you didn't hear that？
(You can have all the confidence in yourself ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Well, I've never had any regrets to have you as my girlfriend, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Manaka
W-What is this all of a sudden...？
Rather,I've been wondering if I'm good enough for you...
Hey, besides you... I've never even thought about anyone else.
Yeah, It's the same for me, too. So, we should both have confidence in ourselves. We're equal now.
Can I really be confident？
Of course！ But... Is it okay that your spirit might rub off on me？
Hehe... It's okay if you're brimming with confidence.
Well then, I should do the same. Otherwise, it'll be unfair ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hehehe！ I understand... From now on, let's do our best together, okay？
Manaka
Do you know the mechanisms of falling in love？
Mechanisms？
Yes. Everything we feel, including heart throbbing or the feelings of happiness, is because of substances in our brain.
Mmm, that's rather blunt...
Isn't it？ It's so scientific that I'm a little disappointed.
It's too much if you think that the way we are is thanks to adrenaline, endorphins and the like.
Hmmm... But, is that really how it is？
What do you mean？
I mean, do people just fall in love because of that？
...I wonder. But somehow, I hope there's something more to it than that...
Manaka
I've decided to stop thinking about it, you know？
...Ah, about the mechanisms of falling in love？
Yeah. Assuming that brain substances are capricious like that... I have that kind of feeling only when I'm with you.
...Because I met you, I fell in love with you. With just that, I'm fine.
Besides, isn't it annoying？ I don't need scientific talk. I can tell that I love you just like this.
Yeah, you could say that.
Hehe, right？
I think, definitely, from now on... I'll grow to love you more and more... You accept that, right？
Yeah, trust me！
Manaka
Say, you're a bit forgetful but... Your birthday is coming up soon, isn't it？
Ah！.. My birthday？
Hehe, yes. Not anyone else's, it's yours.
Really？ Looks like my adulthood is approaching.
To mark the occasion, do you have any requests, like something you want？
Are you going to give me a present？ Let me see it ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
It's okay if it's not right now. So, will you think about it for me？
Sure, I will. But, why do you look so happy？
Well, it's the day my darling was born and I can celebrate it. Why shouldn't I be happy？
Ah, are you embarrassed？ How cute▼
(When it's said right to my face like that, I guess it can't be helped...)
Manaka
Say, have you thought about your request？
Not yet. I really can't decide yet.
Being a young man, you shouldn't keep thinking about it for too long.
Hahaha. On the other hand, do you have anything you want to give me ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Hmm？
Oh, seems like you do.
It's not like I don't have any, but I prefer to give you something you want.
I see...
Because I'm interested in what you'll request. Hehe, I'm looking forward to it, OK▼
(It seems like a difficult hurdle has arisen... Is it just my imagination？)
(I haven't given any thought about my birthday present request yet...)
Manaka
Hey！
Eh！？
Hehe, I can see through you. With that look, you haven't decided what you want yet, right？
Yeah...
Geez, I didn't mean to make you feel troubled like this. Hey, how about you let me pick a present for you？
That way... you don't have to worry about it so much.
Ah... right.
No, it's not good that you have to worry about your own birthday present.
(But, now I have to make sure you don't worry about it too much...)
How is it？ Have you decided what you'd do for my birthday ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
...Hey, now you're totally different.
Hahaha. Of course.
Hehe. Okay, okay. There's some progress. You can look forward to it.
Oh, very confident, huh？
...Yeah. Because I'm the happiest person when it comes to your birthday.
Even more than I am？
Yeah, that's why I'm confident that I can make you happy... Yeah.
Ah, I must be the first one to say Happy Birthday to you. If someone else is about to say it before me, you've got to run away！
...I'll try.
No, you must run away.
Haha, roger that！
Very well. Yeah！ Teehee！
The day of your birthday is getting close, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Manaka
Hmm？ You remembered？
Of course.
Hehe. Thanks. Are you planning something for me？
Um, yeah. Speaking of which, will you have anything special at home？
Yeah, it's marked on the schedule of everyone in my family.
I see. Your family always celebrates birthdays and such, hmm, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
It'll be a big issue if anyone forgets.
So, you mustn't... Ah, but since you mentioned it as early as now, I can rest assured, can't I？
Yeah... I don't think I'll forget...
Teeheehee！
Hey, up until now, what has been the present that you got that you liked most, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
What I liked most is the fountain pen that Papa and Mama gave me when I entered junior high.
Hmm... A fountain pen？
Mama always uses fountain pens. She looks very cool when she writes. I used to imitate her when I was a child.
It felt great when I wrote with a fountain pen, so I used it every day until she found out.
...It wasn't a nice idea to write until the pen nib broke.
Hahaha. That's what I can expect from you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Then my parents gave one to me as a present on the entrance ceremony. But I didn't want to ruin it, so I didn't use it.
That's kind of wasteful...
Yeah, probably. Anyway, is this useful as a reference？
...Who knows？
Hehe！ Do your best, okay？
Have you ever hated your birthday ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
Why？
Sometimes when I mentioned about birthdays to girls, some of them looked depressed.
Hehe. Yeah, I think that happens. But for me, I'm really looking forward to my birthday...
Ah, I can say that it's time to contemplate on different things.
Contemplate？
Yeah, when your birthday arrives, you grow up for another year. It's like you're getting close to becoming an adult, right？
That's true.
This has turned to be such a serious conversation, but I think that's how I feel.
(You really think about things seriously, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Your birthday is getting closer and closer, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Manaka
Yeah. Hey, last time, I told you that I usually contemplate on different things on my birthday, right？
Yeah, sure.
But this year... I don't really think much about it.
Eh...？ Why？
Because you're with me. Just this already makes my heart throb.
I'm sure my birthday this year will turn out to be a great one. One that I'll never forget.
...Hehe！ That's why you should be the first one to say Happy Birthday to me this year. I'll be waiting.
Okay！
Manaka
From that time... Since I confessed my love to you, it's almost been a year.
Really？... Yeah, it was around this time.
It's "already" been a year or "just" a year... I'm not sure how I feel. It's funny how time plays tricks like that.
Yeah.
Hehe. Many things have happened during this one year, huh？
Yeah, so many that I can't possibly count them.
Hey, if the first year has been like this, then how do you think the later years will turn out？
I'm sure much more crazy stuff will happen. Are you ready for it？
Hehe, of course. Let's continue making memories together.
Manaka
Hey, have I... become a proper girlfriend for you？
You're perfect as a girlfriend.
...You answered pretty quickly. Are you sure？
I'm positive. We've done all sorts of things... There are things I couldn't have done if you weren't my girlfriend.
Eh！？ What are you talking about？ Y-You shouldn't be talking about that kind of stuff here...
Stuff like going out on dates and holding hands while we walk...
Hmph... forget it！
(...Why is she so angry？)
Let's continue what we were talking about before...
Manaka
Oh. So, you want to say more weird stuff？
I wasn't going to！ I'm your boyfriend, so I wonder if I'm good enough, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
...Why are you so quiet now？
Hehe, just teasing you. To be honest, I think you're almost too good to be my boyfriend.
It'd be great if you didn't say weird things... But that's what makes you who you are, I suppose？
Please don't ever change▼
(I should be feeling happy to hear this... right？)
Manaka
The countdown to our one year anniversary has started▼
So it has.
Hehe. I know there's a saying "Don't count your chickens before they hatch" but...
Next year, and the years after that, wouldn't it be nice to stay like this？
Yeah, and we'll keep growing together.
Yeah, bit by bit, we're getting there.... Until we finally grow old together.
Forever and ever.
Forever and ever.
Hahaha...
Hehehe...
